§ 40-6-125. Method of giving hand and arm signalsAll signals required by this article when given by hand and arm shall be given from the left side of the vehicle in the following manner and shall indicate as follows:
(1)  Left turn, hand and arm extended horizontally;

(2)  Right turn, hand and arm extended upward;

(3)  Stop or decrease speed, hand and arm extended downward.

